creator: The Peak Community Church
descriptionHtml:
It is our purpose to:

To proclaim the gospel of Jesus Christ without compromise. Preaching the full council of God under the anointing of The Holy Spirit. To see the people in the city of Peekskill come into a personal relationship with God, and to disciple and train them for the work of the ministry. To create an environment where the community can come together in an atmosphere of live worship that will be culturally relevant. To see a community united on the unshakable, immutable, indisputable, inerrant Word of God.
descriptionShort: Come Worship with us at the Peak!
